Class GameState

java.lang.Object
src.GameState
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class GameState
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
This class holds the state of the game and all of its elements. This class also handles user inputs, which affect the game state.
